---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy — ScandiJapandi" description="How ScandiJapandi collects and uses your data.">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-paper px-6 py-32 pt-40">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-stone mb-6">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl text-ink font-light mb-12">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-sm text-stone font-light leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">Who we are</h2>
          <p>ScandiJapandi is operated by SKM Nordic AS, a Norwegian company (org.nr. forthcoming). Our website is <a href="https://scandijapandi.no" class="text-ink underline">scandijapandi.no</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">What data we collect</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-none">
            <li>— Email address (when you join the Private Circle or make a purchase)</li>
            <li>— Name, shipping address, and phone number (when you make a purchase, via Stripe)</li>
            <li>— Language preference and referral source (stored locally in your browser)</li>
            <li>— Basic analytics data (page visits, anonymised)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">How we use it</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-none">
            <li>— To process and fulfil your orders</li>
            <li>— To send you order confirmations and shipping updates</li>
            <li>— To notify you of new arrivals and collections (only with your consent)</li>
            <li>— To improve the website experience</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">Third parties</h2>
          <p>We use Stripe for payment processing, Resend for transactional email, and Netlify for hosting. Each has their own privacy policy. We do not sell your data to any third party.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">Your rights</h2>
          <p>Under GDPR (Norway/EU) and APPI (Japan), you have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data at any time. Contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@scandijapandi.no" class="text-ink underline">privacy@scandijapandi.no</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">Cookies</h2>
          <p>We use essential cookies only. We do not use advertising or tracking cookies. You can reject non-essential cookies using the banner shown on your first visit.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about your data: <a href="mailto:privacy@scandijapandi.no" class="text-ink underline">privacy@scandijapandi.no</a></p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-ink/8">
        <p class="text-xs text-stone/50">Last updated: July 2026 · SKM Nordic AS · Norway</p>
      </div>

      <a href="/" class="inline-block mt-8 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-stone hover:text-ink transition-colors">
        ← Back to collection
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
